<h2 class="nx-font-semibold nx-tracking-tight nx-text-slate-900 dark:nx-text-slate-100 nx-mt-10 nx-border-b nx-pb-1 nx-text-3xl nx-border-neutral-200/70 contrast-more:nx-border-neutral-400 dark:nx-border-primary-100/10 contrast-more:dark:nx-border-neutral-400">总结<a href="#总结" id="总结" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"></a></h2>
<ul class="nx-mt-6 nx-list-disc first:nx-mt-0 ltr:nx-ml-6 rtl:nx-mr-6">
<li class="nx-my-2"><code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">THREE.Shape</code> 用于创建 2D 形状。</li>
<li class="nx-my-2"><code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">ShapeGeometry</code> 直接渲染 2D 形状。</li>
<li class="nx-my-2"><code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">ExtrudeGeometry</code> 可以将 2D 形状拉伸为 3D 物体。</li>
<li class="nx-my-2"><code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">holes</code> 可用于创建镂空形状。</li>
<li class="nx-my-2">可以使用 <code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">lineTo</code>、<code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">moveTo</code>、<code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">bezierCurveTo</code> 等方法定义路径。</li>
